label: Extracts from Geological Works
description: Contains mostly extracts from select Geological Works, and some illustrations.  Geological Works referred to include H[ar]burton on some beds of Shell Marle in Scotland; various authors on Bakie including Blackadder, Ogilvie; Humboldt's Personal Narrative. A number of pages blank, paginated.
